title: Powerball instructional video
description:
This is the video that comes with the Powerball signature series.

It is not really that good, but the records section is not bad, and the disc says `No unauthorised copying or distribution&#039; on it, so I decided to do both.

This is an un-modified and apparently unencrypted (no CSS) plain DVD image. Just play it with your favourite DVD player (preferably one that is free as in freedom, like mplayer (http://www.mplayerhq.hu/design7/news.html) or xine (http://xinehq.de/) ), or just write it to a DVD.
